About Us

Welcome to Doctro! Your healthcare partner, accessible at the touch of a button.

Our Mission

At Doctro, our mission is to make healthcare more accessible and affordable. We bring healthcare services to your fingertips with features like live queue tracking, telemedicine, and emergency services.

Our Vision

Our vision is to bridge the gap between patients and healthcare providers, ensuring that everyone can receive the care they need when they need it.

Why Choose Us?

  • Convenient Online Appointments
  • Real-Time Health Tracking
  • 24/7 Emergency Assistance
  • Experienced Doctors and Specialists
